data.description: Come and see this beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath home with over 2300sqft. This home offers several upgrades from the kitchen to the restrooms. Has a large 2 car garage with plenty of room for your vehicles or just use for extra storage. Beautiful big kitchen with plenty of room for you and the family to spend some quality time making all your favorite dishes. This home has a fenced in front yard with minimal upkeep giving you more time to spend with friends or family. On hot days enjoy the comfort of a nice ice cold refrigerated air with family in comfort watching movies or can just relax after a hard days work. Come and see for yourself what this house has to offer before its gone.
